			<CASNumber>21645-51-2</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Aluminium hydroxide is a white solid typically produced as a by-product in the Bayer process of aluminium production. It has undergone purification, conforms to relevant industry standards, and is used in various applications such as water treatment, as a fire retardant, and in pharmaceuticals. The production route involves the digestion of bauxite ore with caustic soda. It is often found in a production mix and is available in different grades for consumers and manufacturers.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">氢氧化铝是一种白色固体，通常作为铝生产拜耳法的副产品产生。它已经过纯化，符合相关行业标准，用于多种应用，如水处理、作为阻燃剂和制药。其生产路线涉及用烧碱消化铝土矿。它通常以生产混合物的形式存在，供消费者和制造商使用不同等级的产品。</common:generalComment>
